        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Feature 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Secure & Reliable</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Military-grade security with unique QR codes and encrypted data. 
          99.9% uptime ensures your events run smoothly.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>